OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright
OL,6,Fevening to end Sunday, however cloud
OL,7,Fwill build from the north with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain reaching North Wales
OL,9,Fby dawn. Winds falling light away from
OL,10,Fwestern coasts. Feeling chilly with a
OL,11,Frisk of frost under the clearest skies.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FOutbreaks of patchy rain will
OL,14,Fsink south across Wales on Monday,
OL,15,Fclearing to sunny spells during the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Feeling rather chilly for
OL,17,Fthe time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
